  <head>
    <title>爸 设计前期于场地知识总结</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <outline text="设计前期  场地与建筑设计（知识点）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%20%20%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第一节 设计前期（基本概念）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%82%20%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="业主---建筑师---承包商三边关系：业主与建筑师是委托设计的关系，业主与承包商是委托建设的关系，建筑师与承包商是技术指导与服务的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB---%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88---%E6%89%BF%E5%8C%85%E5%95%86%E4%B8%89%E8%BE%B9%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%98%AF%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8E%E6%89%BF%E5%8C%85%E5%95%86%E6%98%AF%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%8E%E6%89%BF%E5%8C%85%E5%95%86%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%8E%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="基本建设：国民经济各部门中，固定资产的再生产以及相关的工作。基本建设的结果是固定资产的增加、维修、改造。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%86%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E3%80%81%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E3%80%81%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="基本建设程序：是指工程项目从策划、评估、决策、设计、施工到竣工验收、投入生产或交付使用的整个建设过程中，各项工作必须遵循的先后工作次序。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%8E%E7%AD%96%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E3%80%81%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%B0%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E3%80%81%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%88%96%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%88%E5%90%8E%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%AC%A1%E5%BA%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建设项目：是指按一个总体规划或设计进行建设的，由一个或若干个互有内在联系的单项工程组成的工程总和。。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%88%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%96%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%92%E6%9C%89%E5%86%85%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E9%A1%B9%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%80%BB%E5%92%8C%E3%80%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="单项工程：是指具有独立的设计文件，建成后能够独立发挥生产能力或使用功能的工程项目。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%95%E9%A1%B9%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E5%90%8E%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%A5%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E6%88%96%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="单位工程：是指具有独立的设计文件，能够独立组织施工，但不能独立发挥生产能力或使用功能的工程项目。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%A5%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E6%88%96%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建设期：是指工程项目从投资决策开始到竣工投产为止，所需要的时间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%8E%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%88%B0%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%95%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%BA%E6%AD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="工程项目周期：包括投资决策、建设实施和运营使用共3个时期，及以下8项主要工作（阶段）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%85%B13%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B8%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%88%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="投资决策：1.项目意向，2.项目建议书（立项），3.可研报告，4.项目评估报告，5.项目审批（可研审批）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%EF%BC%9A1.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C2.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%88%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C3.%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%94%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C4.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C5.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%94%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建设实施：1.设计招标，2.设计任务书，3.工程设计（方案、初步、施工图设计），4.施工准备（施工招标、施工合同、监理合同、施工许可证、用地手续、五通一平等）5.施工实施，6.竣工验收。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%9A1.%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C2.%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C3.%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%81%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C4.%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%88%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E3%80%81%E7%9B%91%E7%90%86%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B8%E5%8F%AF%E8%AF%81%E3%80%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%89%8B%E7%BB%AD%E3%80%81%E4%BA%94%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%895.%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C6.%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="运营使用期：1.运营使用，2.项目后评价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%9A1.%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C2.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="工程项目有3个时期，8项主要工作，3个审批程序。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%9C%893%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C8%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C3%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="3个时期：投资决策、建设实施、运营使用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%9A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="8项主要工作：1.项目建议书（立项），2.可研报告，3.项目评估报告，4.工程设计，5.施工准备，6.施工建设，7.运营使用，8.项目后评价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E8%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%9A1.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%88%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C2.%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%94%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C3.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C4.%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C5.%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C6.%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C7.%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C8.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="3个审批程序：1.项目建议书（立项），2.项目可研审批（确定项目规模、建设条件、投资估算、资金来源、技术方案、运营方式等），3.初步设计审批（项目规模、项目概算、工艺技术、施工条件、施工方案）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9A1.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%88%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C2.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%94%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%EF%BC%88%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E6%9D%A5%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%81%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C3.%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%EF%BC%88%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%A6%82%E7%AE%97%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E8%89%BA%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="《关于基本建设程序的若干规定》将基本建设程序分为以下8项：1.计划任务：2.建设危息的选择；3.设计文件；4.建设准备；5.计划安排；7.生产准备；8.竣工验收与交付生产。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%8B%E5%B0%86%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B8%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%9A1.%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%9A2.%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%B1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%EF%BC%9B3.%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9B4.%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%9B5.%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%EF%BC%9B7.%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%9B8.%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="项目后评价：是王程项目竣工投产、生产运营一段时间后，对项目的立项快策、设计施工、竣工投产、生产运营等全过程进行系统评价的一种技术活动。是固定资产管理的一项重要内容，也是固定资产投资管理的最后一个环节。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%8B%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%95%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%E5%BF%AB%E7%AD%96%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%81%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%95%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E7%AD%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%82%E6%98%AF%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E9%A1%B9%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%8E%AF%E8%8A%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建设项目经济评价：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="（1）建设项目经济评价应根据国民经济与社会发展以及行业、地区发展规划的要求，在项目初步方案的基础上，采用科学的分析方法，对拟建项目的财务可行性和经济合理性进行分析论证，为项目的科学决策提供经济方面的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E4%B8%8E%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A2%E5%8A%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）建设项目经济评价包括财务评价和国民经济评价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%B4%A2%E5%8A%A1%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）建设项目可行性研究阶段的经济评价应系统分析、计算项目的效益和费用，通过多方案经济比选推荐最佳方案。对项目建设的必要性、财务可行性、经济合理性，以及投资风险等进行全面评价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%BA%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%81%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E5%92%8C%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%AF%94%E9%80%89%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%82%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A2%E5%8A%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E7%AD%89%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（4）项目规划、机会研究、项目建议书阶段的经济评价可适当简化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E3%80%81%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（5）对于实行审批制的政府投资项目，应根据政府投资主管部门的要求，按照《建设项目经济评价方法》与《建设项目经济评价参数》执行；对于实行核准制和备案制的企业投资项目，可根据核准机关或备案机关以及投资者的要求，选用建设项目经济评价的方法和相应的参数。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%8E%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%8B%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%9B%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%B3%E6%88%96%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%B3%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%89%E7%94%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（6）建设项目经济评价必须保证评价的客观性、科学性、公正性；坚持定量分析与定性分析相结合、以定量分析为主，以及动态分析与静态分析相结合、以动态分析为主的原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A2%E8%A7%82%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9B%E5%9D%9A%E6%8C%81%E5%AE%9A%E9%87%8F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9A%E9%87%8F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="项目立项：项目经过项目实施组织决策者和政府有关部门的审核或备案，并列入项目实施组织或者政府计划的过程叫项目立项。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E8%80%85%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A1%E6%A0%B8%E6%88%96%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%8F%AB%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="项目立项又被称为“项目建议书审批”；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%E5%8F%88%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="项目立项按其所对应的报批程序，分为备案制、核准制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%E6%8C%89%E5%85%B6%E6%89%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%B9%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E5%88%B6%E3%80%81%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="《国务院关于投资体制改革的决定》国发[209D20号规定：转变政府管理职能，确立企业的投资主体地位。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%A2%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BD%93%E5%88%B6%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%8B%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%91%5B209D20%E5%8F%B7%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9A%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E7%AB%8B%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%B8%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="（1）对于企业不使用政府投资建设的项目，一律不再实行审批制，区别不同情况实行核准制和备案制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%BE%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（2）企业投资建设实行核准制的项目，仅需向政府提交项目申请报告，不再经过批准项目建议书、可行性研究报告和开工报告的程序。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%85%E9%9C%80%E5%90%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E5%92%8C%E5%BC%80%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（3）政府对企业提交的项目申请报告，主要从维护经济安全、合理开发利用资源、保护生态环境、优化重大布局、保障公共利益、防止出现垄断等方面进行核准。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%9E%84%E6%96%AD%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（4）有关实行核准制的项目参见《政府核准投资项目管理办法》（2014年）和《政府核准的投资项目目录》（2016年）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%82%E8%A7%81%E3%80%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%882014%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%882016%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="《企业投资项目核准和备案管理办法》（2017年）的规定：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%B8%E5%87%86%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%882017%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="1.实行备案管理的项目，项目单位应当在开工建设前，通过在线平台将相关信息告知项目备案机关，依法履行投资项目信息告知义务，并遵循诚信和规范原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%9C%A8%E7%BA%BF%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%86%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%B1%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%AA%E8%AF%9A%E4%BF%A1%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="2.项目备案机关应当制定项目备案基本信息格式文本，具体包括以下内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%B3%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（1）项目单位基本情况；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（2）项目名称、建设地点、建设规模、建设内容；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（3）项目总投资额；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%BB%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A2%9D%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（4）项目符合产业政策声明。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（5）项目单位应当对备案项目信息的真实性、合法性和完整性负责。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="设计前期工作：包括项目建议书、项目可研、项目评估、概念设计、设计任务书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%81%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%94%E3%80%81%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E3%80%81%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="项目建议书包括以下内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="（1）投资建设项目的必要性和依据，背景材料，拟建地点的长远规划，行业及地区规划资料；还应包括所在地区的环境现状，可能造成的环境影响分析，当地环境保护部门的意见和委托及存在的问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E9%95%BF%E8%BF%9C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%9B%E8%BF%98%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%81%E5%92%8C%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E5%8F%8A%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（2）产品方案、拟建规模和建设地点的初步设想及论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%81%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E6%83%B3%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（3）资源情况、交通运输及其他建设条件和协作关系的初步分析。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（4）主要工艺技术方案的设想。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E8%89%BA%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E6%83%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（5）投资估算和资金筹措设想。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E5%92%8C%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E7%AD%B9%E6%8E%AA%E8%AE%BE%E6%83%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（6）设计、施工项目及进度安排。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%8A%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（7）经济效果和社会效益的分析与初。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（8）有关的初步结论和建议。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%BB%93%E8%AE%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
          <outline text="可研报告：是建设项目投资决策前进行技术经济论证的一种科学方法。通过对项目有关的工程、技术、环境、经济及社会效益等方面的条件和情况进行调查、研究、分析，对建设项目技术上的先进性、经济上的合理性和建设上的可行性，在多方案分析的基础上作出比较和综合评价，为项目决策提供可靠依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%94%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E5%89%8D%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E3%80%81%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BA%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="1.可行性研究报告的作用：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）建设项目投资决策的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）编制设计文件的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）向银行贷款的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%90%91%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C%E8%B4%B7%E6%AC%BE%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（4）建设单位与各协作单位签订合同和有关协议的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%84%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%AD%BE%E8%AE%A2%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（5）环保部门、规划部门审批项目的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（6）施工组织、工程进度安排及竣工验收的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%8F%8A%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（7）项目后评价的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（8）企业组织管理、机构设置、劳动定员、职工培训等企业管理工作的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%9A%E5%91%98%E3%80%81%E8%81%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%9F%B9%E8%AE%AD%E7%AD%89%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="2.可行性研究报告的内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（1）总论项目建设的必要性和依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%80%BB%E8%AE%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（2）市场预测和建设发展规模。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（3）资源、原材料、燃料及公司配套设施情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E3%80%81%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（4）根据城市规划条件提出场地选址方案的建议。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E9%80%89%E5%9D%80%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（5）项目设计多方案优劣比较。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%A3%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（6）环境保护与劳动生产安全。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%B8%8E%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（7）企业组织机构，各层次管理、技术的劳动定员和相关人员培训。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%84%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%9A%E5%91%98%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E5%9F%B9%E8%AE%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（8）勘察设计工作和工程施工的组织计划及进度要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E5%8B%98%E5%AF%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%8F%8A%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（9）总投资估算和资金筹措计划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%889%EF%BC%89%E6%80%BB%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E5%92%8C%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E7%AD%B9%E6%8E%AA%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（10）社会、环境（含建设项目环境影响报告书或表）及经济评价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8810%EF%BC%89%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%88%E5%90%AB%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E4%B9%A6%E6%88%96%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（11）综合评价与结论、建议。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8811%EF%BC%89%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%93%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
          <outline text="项目评估报告：是对拟建项目的可行性研究报告进行评价。审查项目可行性研究的可靠性、真实性和客观性，对项目投资的最终决策是否可行进行认定，确认最佳投资方案。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%B9%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A2%E8%A7%82%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%A4%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="1.项目评估报告的依据：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）项目建议书及其批准文件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）可行性研究报告。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）报送单位的申请报告及主管部问酶初审意见。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%A5%E9%80%81%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%AE%E9%85%B6%E5%88%9D%E5%AE%A1%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（4）项目（公司）章程、合同及复文件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%EF%BC%89%E7%AB%A0%E7%A8%8B%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%8D%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（5）有关资源、原料、燃料水、电、交通、通信、资金、组织征地、拆迁等项目建设与生产条件的有关批文或协。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E5%8E%9F%E6%96%99%E3%80%81%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E3%80%81%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%BE%81%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E6%8B%86%E8%BF%81%E7%AD%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E6%89%B9%E6%96%87%E6%88%96%E5%8D%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（6）项目资金落实文件及各投资者出具的资金安排的承诺函。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E8%90%BD%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%84%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%80%85%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E7%9A%84%E6%89%BF%E8%AF%BA%E5%87%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（7）项目长期负债和短期借款等文件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E8%B4%9F%E5%80%BA%E5%92%8C%E7%9F%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%80%9F%E6%AC%BE%E7%AD%89%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（8）必备的其他文件和资料。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E5%BF%85%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="2.项目评估报告的内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）项目建设必要性评估。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）项目建设和生产条件评估。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）生产工艺、技术功能、设备等先进性评估。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%B7%A5%E8%89%BA%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%AD%89%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（4）项目效益评估，包括项目财务、经济及社会效益评估。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%B4%A2%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（5）项目总评估，为项目决策提供科学依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%BB%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="3.项目评估报告决策内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）全面审核报告中反映的各项情况是否确定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%A1%E6%A0%B8%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）分析报告中的各项指标是否正确。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）从企业、国家和社会三个方面，综合分析和判断工程项目的经济和社会效益。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%8E%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%92%8C%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（4）分析和判断报告的可靠性、真实性和客观性，对项目给出取舍的结论性意见和建议，最后根据投资额的大小和项目隶属关系，由国家发改委或国务院决策。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%92%8C%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A2%E8%A7%82%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%99%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%96%E8%88%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E8%AE%BA%E6%80%A7%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%81%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A2%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%92%8C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E9%9A%B6%E5%B1%9E%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%91%E6%94%B9%E5%A7%94%E6%88%96%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%A2%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="《环境保护部基本建设项目管理办法》（2012年）对项目前期工作的要求：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%882012%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="1. 根据相关规划，我部建立基本建设项目储备库。有基本建设任务的相关单位（以下简称“项目单位”）应按照国家有关规定，申报纳入我部基本建设项目储备库。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%20%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E9%83%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E5%BA%93%E3%80%82%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%AE%80%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%89%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B3%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B3%E5%85%A5%E6%88%91%E9%83%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E5%BA%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="2. 项目单位应委托具备乙级及以上资质的工程咨询机构，编制项目建议书、可行性研究报告和初步设计，与申报文件一并报送我部。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%20%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E5%85%B7%E5%A4%87%E4%B9%99%E7%BA%A7%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%A8%E8%AF%A2%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E5%92%8C%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%B3%E6%8A%A5%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E9%80%81%E6%88%91%E9%83%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）项目建议书：项目单位根据国家相关规划、行业政策和自身发展需求，编制项目建议书。其主要内容包括：项目建设的必要性、拟建地点、拟建规模、投资估算、资金筹措以及经济、社会、环境效益分析等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E7%AD%B9%E6%8E%AA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）可行性研究报告：项目建议书批准后，项目单位应编制可行性研究报告，其主要内容包括：项目概况、建设的必要性、选址及建没条件、规模及内容、工程技术方案、环境影响评价、消防、职业安全卫生和能源节约筋价、投资估算及资金来源、经济和社会效益分析、建设周期和工程进度安排等。落嗓爷项建设和运行保障条件，并按有关规定取得相关许可、审查意见。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%BA%94%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%A6%82%E5%86%B5%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E9%80%89%E5%9D%80%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E6%B2%A1%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%8F%8A%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%81%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%AD%8B%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%81%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E5%8F%8A%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E6%9D%A5%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E8%90%BD%E5%97%93%E7%88%B7%E9%A1%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%8C%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%AE%B8%E5%8F%AF%E3%80%81%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）初步设计（含概算）：可行慢研究报告批准后，应对建设项目技术方案、工程方案的可靠性和投资规模的合理性进行先化和细化。初步设计应符合国家有关规定和可行性研究报告批复文件的有关要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E5%90%AB%E6%A6%82%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%85%A2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%88%E5%8C%96%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%86%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%BA%94%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%89%B9%E5%A4%8D%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="3. 投资概算超过可行性研究报告批准的估算总投资百分之十，或建设单位、建设性质、建设地点、建设规模、技术方案等发生重大变更的项目，应重新编制和报批可行性研究报告。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%20%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%A6%82%E7%AE%97%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%87%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E6%80%BB%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E7%99%BE%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E5%8D%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%AD%89%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
          <outline text="概念设计：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="是对设计对象的总体布局、功能、形式等进行可能性的构想和分析；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%AD%89%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E6%83%B3%E5%92%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="提出设计概念及创意；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%8F%8A%E5%88%9B%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="是近年来从国外引进的设计方法和程序，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9D%A5%E4%BB%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="常作为大、中型建设项目设计前期工作中对项目的初步研究，以及假想题目的学术性探讨。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9E%8B%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%81%87%E6%83%B3%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A6%E6%9C%AF%E6%80%A7%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="与实施方案不同，项目的概念设计更强调建筑师的设计理念和创意。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E5%92%8C%E5%88%9B%E6%84%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
          <outline text="设计任务书：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="是由建设方编制的工程项目建设大纲，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%B9%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%B2%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="向受托设计单位明确提出拟建项目的设计内容及要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%91%E5%8F%97%E6%89%98%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="是工程设计的主要设计依据，其内容主要有建设规模、功能要求、工艺要求、设备设施水平、装修标准等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E8%89%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%81%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="是确定工程项目和建设方案的基本文件，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="是业主对工程项目设计提出的要求，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E5%AF%B9%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="是设计工作指令性文件，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%80%A7%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="是编制设计文件的主要依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
          <outline text="设计任务书编制的主要依据是：可行性研究报告、国家发布的相关标准及规范、政府部门的相关文件等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B9%A6%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%81%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="设计任务书编制的深度应能满足开展设计的需要。其内容分述如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B9%A6%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E8%83%BD%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%BC%80%E5%B1%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%88%86%E8%BF%B0%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="1.项目概况：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%A6%82%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）项目的名称、位置、组成、规模及设计范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）项目场地现状，包括建设用地范围、地形，场地内原有建筑物、构筑物，要求保留的树木及文物古迹的拆除和保留情况等；此外，还应说明场地周边道路及建筑等环境情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E3%80%81%E6%9E%84%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%91%E6%9C%A8%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%9B%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AD%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）工程所在地区的气象、地理条件和建设场地的工程地质条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%94%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（4）水、电、气、燃料等能源供应情况，公共设施和交通运输条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E3%80%81%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E7%AD%89%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（5）用地、环保、卫生、消防、人防、抗震等要求和资料。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E6%8A%97%E9%9C%87%E7%AD%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（6）材料供应及施工条件等情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%AD%89%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="2.设计依据及必须提供的资料：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E5%8F%8A%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="（1）可行性研究报告（项目的投资情况）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%88%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（2）政府批准设计项目的文号、协议书文号及其有关内容，适用的国家技术标准。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B7%E3%80%81%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E4%B9%A6%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B7%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（3）现状地形图。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="（4）当地建设行政主管部门对项目的规划规定，以及对项目建设区域的总体规划要求等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="3.设计要求：包括" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="基本要求、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="环境要求、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="功能使用要生产工艺要求、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%B7%A5%E8%89%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="配套设施要求、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="规划设计要求、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="建筑设计标准、建筑造型、建筑室内外装修方面的要求、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="主要技术经济指标，以及需要解决的主要问题等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="4.设计成果内客及深度要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8A%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="5.日程安排及设计文件的释交时间要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8A%E4%BA%A4%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="6.责任和义务" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6.%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%92%8C%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
        </outline>
      </outline>
      <outline text="建筑师的定义、职责、权利与义务" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E3%80%81%E8%81%8C%E8%B4%A3%E3%80%81%E6%9D%83%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%8E%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1.建筑师的法律定义：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="建筑师是以建筑学及相关学科的知识以及建筑设计的技能为社会服务的专业人员。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="注册建筑师是指依法取得注册建筑师证书并从事房屋建筑设计及相关业务的人员。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%AF%81%E4%B9%A6%E5%B9%B6%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%8B%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="注册建筑师分为一级注册建筑师和二级注册建筑师。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="2.建筑师的称号:" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%B0%E5%8F%B7:%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="在许多国家，建筑师的称号受到法律保护。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%B0%E5%8F%B7%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="未按法律规定的程序注册而使用建筑师的称号，或承担按法律规定必须由建筑师进行的建筑实践者，均属违法行为。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%AA%E6%8C%89%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%B0%E5%8F%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E6%8C%89%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E7%94%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E8%80%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%9D%87%E5%B1%9E%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="在我国适用的法律为《中华人民共和国注册建筑师条例》及《中华人民共和国注册建筑师条例实施细则》。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%9D%A1%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%8A%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%9D%A1%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%BB%86%E5%88%99%E3%80%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="（三）建筑师的业务范围" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
        </outline>
        <outline text="3.建筑师的业务范围:" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4:%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="注册建筑师的执业范围：建筑设计、建筑设计技术咨询、建筑物调查与鉴定、对本人主持设计的项目进行施工指导和监督，以及国务院建设行政主管部门规定的其他业务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%92%A8%E8%AF%A2%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%8E%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%81%E5%AF%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%BC%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%91%E7%9D%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%A2%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="注册建筑师执行业务，应当加入建筑设计单位（建筑设计单位的资质等级及其业务范围，由国务院建设行政主管部门规定），" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%88%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%A2%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="由建筑设计单位统一接受委托并统一收费。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="4.《中华人民共和国注册建筑师条例实施细则》规定：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%9D%A1%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%BB%86%E5%88%99%E3%80%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="一级注册建筑师的执业范围不受工程项目规模和工程复杂程度的限制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="二级注册建筑师的执业范围只限于承担工程设计资质标准中建设项目设计规模划分表中规定的小型规模的项目。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%8F%AA%E9%99%90%E4%BA%8E%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="注册建筑师的执业范围不得超越其聘用单位的业务范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A%E5%85%B6%E8%81%98%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="注册建筑师的执业范围与其聘用单位的业务范围不符时，个人执业范围服从聘用单位的业务范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%B6%E8%81%98%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%8E%E8%81%98%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="注册建筑师所在单位承担民用建筑设计项目，应当由注册建筑师任工程项目设计主持人或设计总负责人；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E6%B0%91%E7%94%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E7%94%B1%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%BB%BB%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%BB%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="工业建筑设计项目，须由注册建筑师任工程项目建筑专业负责人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E9%A1%BB%E7%94%B1%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%BB%BB%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="凡属工程设计资质标准中建筑工程建设项目设计规模划分表规定的工程项目，在建筑工程设计的主要文件（图纸）中，须由主持该项设计的注册建筑师签字并加盖其执业印章，方为有效。否则设计审查部门不予审查，建设单位不得报建，施工单位不准施工。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%87%A1%E5%B1%9E%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E8%A1%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E9%A1%BB%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E8%AF%A5%E9%A1%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%B6%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%96%E5%85%B6%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E5%8D%B0%E7%AB%A0%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E3%80%82%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%88%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E6%8A%A5%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%86%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="修改经注册建筑师签字盖章的设计文件。应当由原注册建筑师进行；因特殊情况，原注册建筑师不能进行修改的，可以由设计单位的法人代表书面委托其他符合条件的注册建筑师修改，并签字、加盖执业印章，对修改部分承担责任。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E7%BB%8F%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E7%9B%96%E7%AB%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E7%94%B1%E5%8E%9F%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%9B%E5%9B%A0%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%9F%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%B1%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%B9%A6%E9%9D%A2%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%96%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E5%8D%B0%E7%AB%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
      </outline>
      <outline text="《工程勘察设计收费标准》2002年修订本规定：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%8B%98%E5%AF%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%B9%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8B2002%E5%B9%B4%E4%BF%AE%E8%AE%A2%E6%9C%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="建筑、人防工程复杂程度分三级：I级、Ⅱ级、Ⅲ级；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%86%E4%B8%89%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%9AI%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E2%85%A1%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E2%85%A2%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="大型建筑工程指20001m*以上的建筑" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8C%8720001m*%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="中效指5001~20000m2的建筑，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E6%95%88%E6%8C%875001~20000m2%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="小型指5000m2以下的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E6%8C%875000m2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="各阶段设计深度及内容要求简述：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%84%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%AE%80%E8%BF%B0%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="建筑设计可划分为以下四个阶段：方案设计、初步设计、施工图设计、施工阶段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AA%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="1.方案设计阶段：根据业主提出的项目及投资限额以及建设条件，提供初步的设计方案及工程估价。应满足编制初步设计文件的需要，应满足方案审批或报批的需要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9A%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%99%90%E9%A2%9D%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E4%BC%B0%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%E5%BA%94%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E6%88%96%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="方案设计文件应包括下列内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（1）设计说明书，包括各专业设计说明以及投资估算等内容；对于涉及建筑节能、环保、绿色建筑、人防等设计的专业，其设计说明应有相应的专门内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%90%84%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E7%AD%89%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9B%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（2）总平面图以及相关建筑设计图纸（若为城市区域供热或区域燃气调压站，应提供热能动力专业的设计图纸）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%BE%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E6%88%96%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%87%83%E6%B0%94%E8%B0%83%E5%8E%8B%E7%AB%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（3）设计委托或设计合同中规定的透视图、鸟瞰图、模型等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98%E6%88%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%E9%B8%9F%E7%9E%B0%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="2.初步设计阶段：在深入研究的基础上，提出总平面布置及建筑设计图，确定设计构造、设备及外观，提出总的说明及概算。应满足编制施工图设计文件的需要，应满足初步设计审批的需要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E6%80%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8A%E6%A6%82%E7%AE%97%E3%80%82%E5%BA%94%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="初步设计文件应包括下列内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（1）设计说明书，包括设计总说明、各专业设计说明。对于涉及建筑节能、环保、绿色建筑、人防、装配式建筑等，其设计说明应有相应的专项内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%BB%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E5%90%84%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E3%80%82%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（2）有关专业的设计图纸。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（3）主要设备或材料表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%88%96%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（4）工程概算书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A6%82%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="（5）有关专业计算书（计算书不属于必须交付的设计文件，但应按本规定相关条款的要求编制）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E6%9C%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="3.施工图设计阶段：在初步设计得到批准以后，进行施工图设计。施工图文件应满足设备材料采购、非标准设备制作和施工的需要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%94%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E9%87%87%E8%B4%AD%E3%80%81%E9%9D%9E%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%92%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="施工图设计文件应包括下列内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（1）合同要求所涉及的所有专业的设计图纸（命图纸目录、说明和必要的设备、材料表）以及图纸总封面；对于涉及建筑节能设计的业，其设计说明应有建筑节能设计的专项内容；涉及装配式建筑设计的专业，其设说明及图纸应有装配式建筑专项设计内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%89%80%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%EF%BC%88%E5%91%BD%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E3%80%81%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%92%8C%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E3%80%81%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%80%BB%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9B%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9B%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8A%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）合同要求的工程预算书" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A2%84%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="对于方案设计后直接进入施工图设计的项目，若合同未要求编制工程预算书，施工图设计文件应包括工程概算书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%90%8E%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%8B%A5%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A2%84%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A6%82%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）各专业计算书" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%90%84%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="计算书不属于必须交付的设计文件，但应按本规定相关条款的要求编制并归档保存。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E6%9C%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%B9%B6%E5%BD%92%E6%A1%A3%E4%BF%9D%E5%AD%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="4.施工阶段的主要工作：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（1）在施工前，帮助业主拟订合同文件；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%8B%9F%E8%AE%A2%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）在施工期间，对承包商的工作进行一般性管理，核查工程造价，签发付款证明，核对承包方提出的加工详图，对施工精度、材料及设施提出可接受的标准，定期视察工地，确定基本完工日期；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E6%89%BF%E5%8C%85%E5%95%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%80%A7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B8%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%E7%AD%BE%E5%8F%91%E4%BB%98%E6%AC%BE%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%AF%B9%E6%89%BF%E5%8C%85%E6%96%B9%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%A5%E8%AF%A6%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%AF%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E8%A7%86%E5%AF%9F%E5%B7%A5%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%8C%E5%B7%A5%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）在工程全部完工后，参与竣工验收。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="5.专项设计要求：《建筑工程设计文件编制深度规定》（2016年版）新增加了专项设计，下列四项内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%882016%E5%B9%B4%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E5%9B%9B%E9%A1%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="建筑幕墙设计；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B9%95%E5%A2%99%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="基坑支护设计；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E5%9D%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8A%A4%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="建筑智能化设计；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="预制混凝土构件加工图设计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A2%84%E5%88%B6%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="文件编制深度规定的2016年版与2008年版相比，主要变化如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%842016%E5%B9%B4%E7%89%88%E4%B8%8E2008%E5%B9%B4%E7%89%88%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（1）新增绿色建筑技术应用的内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）新增装配式建筑设计的内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）新增建筑设备控制的相关规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（4）新增建筑节能设计要求，包括各相关专业的设计文件和计算书深度要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%90%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B9%A6%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（5）新增结构工程超限设计可行性论证报告内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%B6%85%E9%99%90%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（6）新增建筑幕墙、基坑支护及建筑智能化专项设计内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B9%95%E5%A2%99%E3%80%81%E5%9F%BA%E5%9D%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8A%A4%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（7）根据建筑工程项目在审批、施工等方面对设计文件深度要求的变化，对原规定中的部分条款作了修改，使之更加适用于目前的工程项目设计，尤其是民用建筑工程项目设计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%AF%B9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%8E%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%86%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B4%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%A4%E5%85%B6%E6%98%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%94%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="注册建筑师的权利：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%83%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="1.注册建筑师有权以注册建筑师的名义执行注册建筑师业务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%9C%89%E6%9D%83%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E4%B9%89%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="2.非注册建筑师不得以注册建筑师的名义执行注册建筑师业务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E4%B9%89%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="3.二级注册建筑师不得以一级注册建筑师的名义执行业务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E4%B9%89%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="4.二级注册建筑师不得超越国家规定的二级注册建筑师的执业范围执行业务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（1）国家规定的一定跨度、跨径和高度以上的房屋建筑，应当由注册建筑师进行设计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%B7%A8%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E8%B7%A8%E5%BE%84%E5%92%8C%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E7%94%B1%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）任何单位和个人修改注册建筑师的设计图纸，应当征得该注册建筑师同意，但是，因特殊情况不能征得该注册建筑师同意的除外。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%BE%81%E5%BE%97%E8%AF%A5%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%81%E5%BE%97%E8%AF%A5%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="注册建筑师应当履行下列义务：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%A5%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（1）遵守法律、法规和职业道德，维护社会公共利益。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%81%B5%E5%AE%88%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E6%B3%95%E8%A7%84%E5%92%8C%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）保证建筑设计的质量，并在其负责的设计图纸上签字。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%B6%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E4%B8%8A%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）保守在执业中所知悉的单位和个人的秘密。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（4）不得同时受聘于两个以上建筑设计单位执行业务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%97%E8%81%98%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（5）不得准许他人以本人名义执行业。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%87%86%E8%AE%B8%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8D%E4%B9%89%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建筑师的其他服务：8项服务，内容如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%9A8%E9%A1%B9%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（1）建筑策划：此项工作的主要任务就是通过对场址及建设任务的详细分析，就建筑项目的功能、形式、时间、投资额等提出合理的综合方案，并以此作为设计的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AD%96%E5%88%92%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A4%E9%A1%B9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%AF%B9%E5%9C%BA%E5%9D%80%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E9%A2%9D%E7%AD%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%A4%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）协助业主拟订设计任务书：收集有关建设资料，研究有关法律、财务及土地利用等问题，测绘现有建筑，编写有关文件，参与业主与主管部门或投资方进行的洽谈等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%8F%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%8B%9F%E8%AE%A2%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A2%E5%8A%A1%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%AD%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E6%B5%8B%E7%BB%98%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E6%88%96%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%BD%E8%B0%88%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）进行项目的使用后评估或称“后评价”（通常在建成后一年保证期结束前）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E6%88%96%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E5%90%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E6%9C%9F%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（4）建筑设计单位签发设计变更（设计变更通知单及附图）注：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%AD%BE%E5%8F%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E5%8D%95%E5%8F%8A%E9%99%84%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%89%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="设计单位负责签发“设计变更”；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E7%AD%BE%E5%8F%91%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="施工单位负责签发“工程洽商”并最终编制竣工图；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E7%AD%BE%E5%8F%91%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%B4%BD%E5%95%86%E2%80%9D%E5%B9%B6%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="业主单位签发“现场签证”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%BB%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%AD%BE%E5%8F%91%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%BE%E8%AF%81%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="（5）设计固定及活动家具、景观小品等" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%8A%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E3%80%81%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E5%B0%8F%E5%93%81%E7%AD%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（6）提供对现有旧建筑的安全条件、价值、维护及改造方面的咨询" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%AF%B9%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%89%E6%97%A7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E3%80%81%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%92%A8%E8%AF%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（7）对某些争端、仲裁提供资料文件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E6%9F%90%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%89%E7%AB%AF%E3%80%81%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（8）提供专业咨询" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E5%92%A8%E8%AF%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建筑工程设计招标投标：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="是设计前期工作的最后环节；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E7%8E%AF%E8%8A%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="“中标人的确定”标志着设计单位（团队）正式进行建筑工程设计的开始，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%AD%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E2%80%9D%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E7%9D%80%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%EF%BC%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="有下列情形之一的，可以不进行招标：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E6%83%85%E5%BD%A2%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8D%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="（1）采用不可替代的专利或者专有技术的；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E4%B8%93%E6%9C%89%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（2）对建筑艺术造型有特殊要求，并经有关主管部门批准的；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E6%9C%89%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%8F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（3）建设单位依法能够自行设计的；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（4）建筑工程项目的改建、扩建或者技术改造，需要由原设计单位设计，否则将影响功能配套要求的；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%81%E6%89%A9%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%94%B1%E5%8E%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E5%B0%86%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="（5）国家规定的其他特殊情形。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E6%83%85%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="建筑工程设计招标形式：公开招标、邀请招标。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%80%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E3%80%81%E9%82%80%E8%AF%B7%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="建筑工程设计招标可以采用：设计方案招标、设计团队招标，招标人可以根据项目特点和实际需要选择。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="设计方案招标，是指主要通过对投标人提交的设计方案进行评审确定中标人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%AF%B9%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AF%84%E5%AE%A1%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="设计团队招标，是指主要通过对投标人拟派设计团队的综合能力进行评审确定中标人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%AF%B9%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%9F%E6%B4%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AF%84%E5%AE%A1%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="公开招标的，招标人应当发布招标公告" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%80%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="邀请招标的，招标人应当向3个以上潜在投标人发出投标邀请书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%82%80%E8%AF%B7%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%90%913%E4%B8%AA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E6%BD%9C%E5%9C%A8%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E9%82%80%E8%AF%B7%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="招标公告或者投标邀请书应当载明招标人称和地址、招标项目的基本要求、投标人的资质要求以及获取招标文件的办法等事项。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E9%82%80%E8%AF%B7%E4%B9%A6%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E8%BD%BD%E6%98%8E%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%B0%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E3%80%81%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="招标人一般应当将建筑工想的方案设计、初步设计和施工图设计一并招标。确需另行选择设计单位承担初步设计、施工图设计的，应当在招标公告或者投标邀请书中明确。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%B0%86%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B6%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E3%80%82%E7%A1%AE%E9%9C%80%E5%8F%A6%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%A8%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E9%82%80%E8%AF%B7%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="鼓励建筑工程实施设计总包。实行设计总包的，按照合同约定或者经招标人同意，设计单位可以不通过招标方式将建筑工程非主体部分的设计进行分包。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%BC%93%E5%8A%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%BB%E5%8C%85%E3%80%82%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%BB%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E7%BA%A6%E5%AE%9A%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E7%BB%8F%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%B0%86%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%BB%E4%BD%93%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%86%E5%8C%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="第十条招标文件应当满足设计方案招标或者设计团队招标的不同需求，主要包括以下内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E6%9D%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="招标文件主要包括以下内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（1）项目基本情况；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（2）城乡规划和城市设计对项目的基本要求；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AF%B9%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（3）项目工程经济技术要求；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（4）项目有关基础资料；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（5）招标内容；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（6）招标文件答疑、现场踏勘安排；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%AD%94%E7%96%91%E3%80%81%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E8%B8%8F%E5%8B%98%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（7）投标文件编制要求；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（8）评标标准和方法；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（9）投标文件送达地点和截止时间；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%889%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%80%81%E8%BE%BE%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（10）开标时间和地点；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8810%EF%BC%89%E5%BC%80%E6%A0%87%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（11）拟签订合同的主要条款；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8811%EF%BC%89%E6%8B%9F%E7%AD%BE%E8%AE%A2%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（12）设计费或者计费方法；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8812%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B4%B9%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E8%AE%A1%E8%B4%B9%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="（13）未中标方案补偿办法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8813%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%AA%E4%B8%AD%E6%A0%87%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="评标由评标委员会负责：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E7%94%B1%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
              <outline text="评标委员会由招标人代表和有关专家组成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E7%94%B1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="评标委员会人数为5人以上单数，其中技术和经济方面的专家不得少于成员总数的2/3。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%BA5%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%95%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E6%80%BB%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%842/3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="建筑工程设计方案评标时，建筑专业专家不得少于技术和经济方面专家总数的2/3" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%80%BB%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%842/3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
              <outline text="投标人或者与投标人有利害关系的人员不得参加评标委员会。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%95%E6%A0%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E5%AE%B3%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%8F%82%E5%8A%A0%E8%AF%84%E6%A0%87%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            </outline>
          </outline>
        </outline>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="第二节  城乡规划与城市设计知识" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%8A%82%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一、城乡规划知识及规范要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="现代城市规划设计思想简述" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%AE%80%E8%BF%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="1.新城市主义：新城市主义”理论与方法是针对西方城市大规模郊区化趋势中浪费土地、破坏自然生态环境和地域景观而提出的。提倡创造和重建丰富多样、适于步行、紧凑且混合使用的社区，对建筑环境进行重新整合，形成完善的都市、城镇、乡村和邻里单元。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E1.%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E9%83%8A%E5%8C%BA%E5%8C%96%E8%B6%8B%E5%8A%BF%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%AA%E8%B4%B9%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E8%80%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%E6%8F%90%E5%80%A1%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E5%92%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E3%80%81%E9%80%82%E4%BA%8E%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%81%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E4%B8%94%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E3%80%81%E4%B9%A1%E6%9D%91%E5%92%8C%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="传统邻里社区发展理论（TND），由安德鲁·杜安尼和伊丽莎白·普拉特-兹伯格提出，代表作品是位于美国马里兰州的肯特兰镇（Kentlands）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%88TND%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%B7%E9%B2%81%C2%B7%E6%9D%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%B0%BC%E5%92%8C%E4%BC%8A%E4%B8%BD%E8%8E%8E%E7%99%BD%C2%B7%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%89%E7%89%B9-%E5%85%B9%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E5%B7%9E%E7%9A%84%E8%82%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%85%B0%E9%95%87%EF%BC%88Kentlands%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="公共交通主导型开发理论（TOD），由彼得·卡尔索普提出，卡尔索普设计的西拉古纳住区位于美国加利福尼亚州萨克拉门托，采用了“步行口袋”概念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%BB%E5%AF%BC%E5%9E%8B%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%88TOD%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%C2%B7%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E7%B4%A2%E6%99%AE%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E7%B4%A2%E6%99%AE%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%A5%BF%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%A4%E7%BA%B3%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E7%A6%8F%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E5%B7%9E%E8%90%A8%E5%85%8B%E6%8B%89%E9%97%A8%E6%89%98%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%8B%E2%80%9D%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="2.紧凑城市：1973年乔治·伯纳德·丹齐格出版的《紧凑城市——适于居住的城市环境计划》及1990年欧共体委员会（CEC）发表的《城市环境绿皮书》，提出紧凑城市作为“一种解决居住和环境问题的途径”的理论。紧凑伦敦规划是欧洲紧凑城市理论的实践代表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E2.%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A1973%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%94%E6%B2%BB%C2%B7%E4%BC%AF%E7%BA%B3%E5%BE%B7%C2%B7%E4%B8%B9%E9%BD%90%E6%A0%BC%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%80%82%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%8A1990%E5%B9%B4%E6%AC%A7%E5%85%B1%E4%BD%93%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%88CEC%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%BB%BF%E7%9A%AE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%94%E5%BE%84%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%98%AF%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="紧凑城市理论主要提倡以下三种做法：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%8F%90%E5%80%A1%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="高密度开发；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E9%AB%98%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="混合的土地利用；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="优先发展公共交通。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
            <outline text="紧凑伦敦规划是欧洲紧凑城市理论的实践代表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%98%AF%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          </outline>
        </outline>
        <outline text="3.城市更新：西方城市更新运动，由单纯的物质环境更新转向对社区邻里环境的综合整治和社区邻里活力的恢复振兴，从大拆大建逐步转变为小规模、分阶段、谨慎渐进式的物质环境改善方式；强调城市更新是一个连续不断的过程。“巴塞罗那奥运村”是城市更新理论的典型代表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%9A%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%BD%AC%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%95%B4%E6%B2%BB%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E6%8C%AF%E5%85%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E5%A4%A7%E6%8B%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E5%B0%8F%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%81%E8%B0%A8%E6%85%8E%E6%B8%90%E8%BF%9B%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9B%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E3%80%82%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E7%BD%97%E9%82%A3%E5%A5%A5%E8%BF%90%E6%9D%91%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="4.精明增长：为应对城市无序蔓延产生的问题，1994年，美国规划师协会提出了“精明增长”的概念。通过规划紧凑型社区，充分发挥已有基础设施的效力，提供多样化的交通和住房选择，来控制城市蔓延，其基本原则有10项。波特兰城市袋展边界控制规划是美国精明增长理论的实践代表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E4.%E7%B2%BE%E6%98%8E%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BA%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A0%E5%BA%8F%E8%94%93%E5%BB%B6%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C1994%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%88%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E7%B2%BE%E6%98%8E%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E5%9E%8B%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%A5%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%BF%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%9D%A5%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%94%93%E5%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E6%9C%8910%E9%A1%B9%E3%80%82%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%B9%E5%85%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A2%8B%E5%B1%95%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%98%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%B2%BE%E6%98%8E%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="（二）城乡规划体系" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="城乡规划以可持续发展思想为理念，通过空间规划、政策制定、社会治理、市场引导、实施管理等途径，促进城乡社会公和经济发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%BA%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E3%80%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%AD%89%E9%80%94%E5%BE%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%83%E8%BF%9B%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="规划设计是城乡规划和城市设计的组成部分，分为区域层面、城市层面、街区层面以及村镇层面等不同的空间层次。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%81%E8%A1%97%E5%8C%BA%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%9D%91%E9%95%87%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="城乡规划包括城镇体系规划《城市规划、镇规划、乡规划和村庄规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="城市规划分为总体规划和详细规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="详细规划分为控制性详细规划和修建性详细规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="城市空间结构分为集中式（网格状、环形放射状）和分散式（指状、带状、组团状）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E7%BD%91%E6%A0%BC%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%BD%A2%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%84%E7%8A%B6%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E6%8C%87%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%A2%E7%8A%B6%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
      </outline>
      <outline text="（三）城市用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》GB50137-2011（节选）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8BGB50137-2011%EF%BC%88%E8%8A%82%E9%80%89%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="3  用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E3%20%20%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="3.1一般规定：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E3.1%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="用地分类包括城乡用地分类、城市建设用地分类两部分，应按土地使用的主要性质进行划分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="用地分类采用大类、中类和小类3级分类体系。大类应采用英文字母表示，中类和小类应采用英文字母和阿拉伯数字组合表示。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB3%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E5%BA%94%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB%E5%BA%94%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E5%92%8C%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="使用本分类时，可根据工作性质、工作内容及工作深度的不同要求，采用本分类的全部或部分类别。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%88%96%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="3.2城乡用地分类：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E3.2%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="城乡用地共分为2大类、9中类、14小类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%B1%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA2%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%819%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%8114%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="城乡用地分类和代码应符合表3.2.2的规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%BA%94%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E8%A1%A83.2.2%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="城乡用地分类和代码表3.2.2类别代码" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A1%A83.2.2%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="大类--字母，中类--字母+数字，小类---字母+数字+数字" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-blue%22%3E%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB--%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB--%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D+%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB---%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D+%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97+%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
